Izangoma zezulu zixwayisa izakhamuzi zaKwaZulu-Natal ngesimo sezulu esingesihle ngempelasonto. Kulindeleke ukuthi kube nomsinga obandayo ozoletha imvula enamandla namakhaza. Lo msinga kulindeleke ukuthi uqhamuke ngasentshonalanga yezwe kusukela namuhla ebusuku, usabalale maphakathi nezwe kusasa, ufudukele ezindaweni ezingasempumalanga ngoMgqibelo. Nasi isimo sezulu sakusasa: